{
  "stem": "26022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And though I was never politically active and neither were my parents, we were always very aware of what went on and, and politically knowledgeable, to a certain extent.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, of course, I formed these wonderful friendships in, in school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had always wanted sisters and brothers and uncles and aunts and cousins.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, I had uncles and aunts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the cousins were-- I had two male cousins 10, 14 years older than myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and then I had, on my mother's side, a 10-year-younger girl cousin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there was no age group that I really belonged to until I got to school and, and had this chance to meet children from intellectual houses and homes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there are friendships that I treasured.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, at my age, there are not many left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I still have a childhood friend who now lives in Florida.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we are like sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She also was an only child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Austria was a Catholic country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] most, or many of them, were Catholic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then this gave us Jewish students-- and there was a large contingent of Jewish girls and two or three Protestants-- Protestants were not very numerous in Austria in those days-- a chance to get our religious education as part of the school curriculum.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the Holy See had a, a pact or whatever you call it with the Austrian government that religion has to be taught during school hours, meaning Catholic religion.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what we are going to do with the others?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a rabbi was brought in twice a week, an hour at a time, to teach us the basics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a priest was brought in for the two or three Protestant students.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
